name: Aqua Crucifix Suncatcher
description:
Oh, how beautiful the sunlight shines through this lovely cross.

This beaded crucifix is wrapped with wire and measures 2 1/2" by 2".

It comes in a clear-lidded white gift box.

A lovely gift for a baptism or confirmation.

name: Baby Braided Beaded Halo Headband
description:
Your darling baby will have a halo!

This braided headband is handknitted and embellished with a crochet heart with a single glass bead in the center.  It is the perfect Valentine gift for your precious baby girl...

It measures 18 inches and is made of polyester and acrylic yarns.  

Handwashing is recommended.

options.name: I can knit this in other colors and sizes.  Please email me.

name: Crystal Beaded Cross
description:
This is a lovely crystal cross using glass seed beads and wire with which to wrap it.  The cross is approximately 2" x 2 1/2".  The Swarovski crystal beads are 10mm rounds.  The wire used may be silver, gold or copper and is tarnish resistant.

The cross may be used as a suncatcher or rear view mirror hanger.  The sunlight passing through the crystal is exquisite.

The cross is displayed in a clear-lidded gift box.
